Code: EXEC SQL SELECT NUM_PESSOA, SEQ_EMAIL, DTH_CADASTRAMENTO, DES_EMAIL, STA_EMAIL, STA_CORRESPONDER, STA_CONTATO, IND_ELETRONICO FROM ODS.OD_PESSOA_EMAIL WHERE NUM_PESSOA = :NUM_PESSOA AND DES_EMAIL = :DES_EMAIL AND STA_EMAIL = :STA_EMAIL AND STA_CORRESPONDER = :STA_CORRESPONDER AND STA_CONTATO = :STA_CONTATO AND IND_ELETRONICO = :IND_ELETRONICO ORDER BY SEQ_EMAIL DESC END SQL
